#: templates/edit.html:8
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Ko‘rsatiladigan ism"

#: templates/edit.html:16
msgid "Weight"
msgstr "Og&#39;irligi"

#: templates/edit.html:19
msgid "This assigns an integer value representing the weight of this problem"
msgstr ""
"Bu muammoning qiyinligini ifodalovchi butun sonni qiymatini belgilaydi"

#: templates/edit.html:24
msgid "Max Attempts"
msgstr "Maksimal urinishlar soni"

#: templates/edit.html:27
msgid ""
"This assigns an integer value representing the maximum number of times a "
"student can attempt the problem"
msgstr ""
"Talaba ushbu muammoni yechishga urinishi mumkin bo‘lgan maksimal urinishlar "
"sonini ifodalovchi butun son qiymatini belgilaydi."

